sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as Auth API
    participant Security as Security Module
    participant Users as Users Collection

    Client->>API: POST /register (email, password)
    API->>Security: hash_password(password)
    API->>Users: insert user document
    API->>Security: create_access_token(sub=email)
    API-->>Client: 201 access_token + user

    Client->>API: POST /login (email, password)
    API->>Users: find_one(email)
    API->>Security: verify_password(plain, hash)
    API->>Security: create_access_token(sub=email)
    API-->>Client: 200 access_token + user

    Client->>API: GET /me (Bearer token)
    API->>Security: decode_access_token(token)
    API->>Users: find_one(email=sub)
    API-->>Client: 200 user OR 401
